r the newsletter signup (blank = email fallback)"},{"key":"tagline_en","value":"The sound of Lingnan, the stage of London","note":"Strapline (English)"},{"key":"tagline_zh","value":"粵韻飄香 · 揚聲倫敦","note":"Strapline (中文)"},{"key":"motto_zh","value":"傳情以藝，化人以文","note":"Association motto"}],"learn":[],"news":[],"social":[{"id":"soci-mqpgihoi","order":1,"platform":"Rednote","url":"asdadad"},{"id":"soci-mqpgiewi","order":2,"platform":"Instagram","url":"asdadasd"}],"about":[{"key":"_diag_test","en":"diagnostic 2026-06-22T19:46:28.679Z","zh":"診斷測試"},{"key":"head_title","en":"Carrying Cantonese opera to a London stage","zh":"把粵劇帶到倫敦舞台"},{"key":"head_intro","en":"Yuet Wan London is a non-profit cultural association dedicated to preserving and sharing the living art of Cantonese opera and music in the United Kingdom.","zh":"倫敦粵韻曲藝文化協會是一個非牟利文化團體，致力在英國保存及傳承粵劇與粵樂這門活的藝術。"},{"key":"quote","en":"“To convey feeling through art, and to cultivate people through culture.”","zh":"「傳情以藝，化人以文。」"},{"key":"mission","en":"Cantonese opera — 粵劇 — is a UNESCO-recognised art form that weaves together song, music, movement and storytelling refined over centuries in the Lingnan region of southern China.\n\nThrough performances, workshops and community events, we bring artists and audiences together — supporting practitioners in the UK while introducing new audiences to its beauty.","zh":"粵劇是聯合國教科文組織認定的藝術形式，融合唱、做、唸、打，於嶺南地區歷經數百年淬煉而成。\n\n透過演出、工作坊與社區活動，我們連繫藝術家與觀眾 —— 既支持在英的從業者，亦向新觀眾介紹粵劇之美。"},{"key":"do1_title","en":"Performances","zh":"舞台演出"},{"key":"do1_text","en":"Staging full Cantonese opera productions and music evenings with live ensemble accompaniment.","zh":"舉辦完整的粵劇演出及粵樂晚會，並以現場樂隊伴奏。"},{"key":"do2_title","en":"Workshops & classes","zh":"工作坊與課程"},{"key":"do2_text","en":"Hands-on sessions in singing, movement and percussion for newcomers and enthusiasts of all ages.","zh":"為各年齡層的初學者及愛好者，提供唱腔、身段及擊樂的實作課程。"},{"key":"do3_title","en":"Community","zh":"社區連繫"},{"key":"do3_text","en":"Talks, demonstrations and cultural exchanges that connect the heritage with new generations in the UK.","zh":"透過講座、示範及文化交流，把這份傳統承傳予英國的新世代。"},{"key":"story_lead","en":"Showcase 2025 — our first full production on a London stage.","zh":"《粵韻飄香揚英倫 2025》 —— 我們在倫敦舞台的首場大型演出。"},{"key":"story_body","en":"In September 2025 we presented our inaugural showcase at the Shaw Theatre in London: a thirteen-segment programme of classic Cantonese opera excerpts and music, performed by visiting and UK-based artists.","zh":"2025 年九月，我們於倫敦邵氏劇院呈獻首場演出：十三個經典粵劇選段及粵樂節目，由訪英及在英藝術家共同演出。"},{"key":"stat1_num","en":2025,"zh":2025},{"key":"stat1_label","en":"Founded","zh":"成立"},{"key":"stat2_num","en":13,"zh":13},{"key":"stat2_label","en":"Programme segments","zh":"演出節目"},{"key":"stat3_num","en":"20+","zh":"20+"},{"key":"stat3_label","en":"Artists & musicians","zh":"藝術家與樂師"},{"key":"stat4_num","en":"UK","zh":"UK"},{"key":"stat4_label","en":"London based","zh":"立足倫敦"},{"key":"cta_title","en":"Be part of the next performance","zh":"參與下一場演出"},{"key":"cta_text","en":"Whether you'd like to perform, learn, volunteer or support — we'd love to hear from you.","zh":"無論您希望演出、學習、做義工或支持我們，都歡迎與我們聯絡。"}],"ok":true,"version":"forms-v3"}